Dan Hicks (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dan_Hicks_(actor) 0 Dan Hicks (sometimes credited as Danny Hicks) is an American actor. Hicks is best known for starring roles in Evil Dead II, Darkman and Intruder as well as appearing in various other horror films.Hicks has a number of roles in director Sam Raimi's films.
